Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper focuses on improving machine translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) falling under cs.CL. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new variant of RNNs to enhance the performance of hybrid models, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with improving the performance of neural networks, which is a subfield of AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a new variant of RNNs, which is a type of neural network. 
5. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - Although the paper does not directly deal with computer vision, the proposed approach of modeling hierarchical structure can be applied to other tasks falling under cs.CV, such as image captioning.
